prodNameC: 卡蒂雅幽門螺旋桿菌IgA抗體檢測試劑組
ingredientsDesc:
1.	Helicobacter pylori antigen (inactivated) coated microasay plate
2.	Serum Diluent Type 1
3.	Calibrator: Human serum or defibrinated plasma.
4.	High Positive Control: Human serum or defibrinated plasma.
5.	Low Positive Control: Human serum or defibrinated plasma.
6.	Negative Control: Human serum or defibrinated plasma.
7.	Horseradish-peroxidase (HRP) Conjugate: Goat anti-human IgA
8.	Chromogen/Substrate Solution Type I: Tetramethylbenzidine (TMB)
9.	Wash Buffer Type I: Contains TBS, Tween-20 and proclin (0.1%) as a preservatives.
10.	Stop Solution: Contains a 1N H2SO4 solution
applicantAddr: 新北市板橋區民生路一段三三號六樓之五
efficacy: 檢測人體血清中幽門螺旋桿菌之抗體IgA。
